{"tid":709640,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"在單親家庭中長大既你請入黎","createTime":"2018-06-20T07:34:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T13:57:32.000Z","uid":113678,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"fd338e983d5158b8132d9dc648b82af3c7c162e5","tid":709640,"uid":113678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T07:34:20.000Z","msg":"細細個以為冇咩野 少一個人 屋企鬆動d<br />\n大個左先發覺原來好有問題<br />\n睇見人地屋企齊齊整整開飯 去飲茶<br />\n自己就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當至親既人都唔愛你既時候<br />\n生活仲有咩意義？"},{"pid":"199df9c70648e17883f3ce8215e303735af7fe62","tid":709640,"uid":85253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T07:40:00.000Z","msg":"咁就當養少一個人<br />\n最緊要係對自己好啲"},{"pid":"da444b8cb95d23cb74d3207b91b8eb2072adefd7","tid":709640,"uid":104171,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T07:46:57.000Z","msg":"下 你仲有fd架嘛<br />\n生活仲有好多意義<br />\n例如食好味嘅野<br />\n<br />\n搵個女朋友啦"},{"pid":"466b3e1e5cb6a0c686a111356a287ececd187f04","tid":709640,"uid":71726,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T07:52:58.000Z","msg":"無感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7193d3b24edd113524e7e64723f5af6128a53ac4","tid":709640,"uid":15558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T07:53:24.000Z","msg":"俾返啲目標自己啦<br />\n<br />\n生存同生活嘅意義都係自己賦與俾自己架<br />\n<br />\n上天拎走咗父母其中一邊嘅愛<br />\n<br />\n你咪去學下愛人等更多嘅人得到愛"},{"pid":"e28ea16daac311242e8972f7928f827da1258170","tid":709640,"uid":119174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T07:56:45.000Z","msg":"小學已經開始無感覺亦覺得無必要見<br />\n想見我就要佢約 問掛唔掛住咪話掛住囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed87966e292c983fbc603fc55314583cbbda5198","tid":709640,"uid":7125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T07:57:00.000Z","msg":"大部分分時間都無感覺<br />\n<br />\n但係一到啲特別時候就有啲hard feeling <br />\n<br />\n例如由細到大啲親子旅行 雙親節 出席各大飲宴 上堂講家庭關係<br />\n<br />\n甚至大個申請grant loan都要報單親 仲比人係咁覆核 死亡證/離婚證書每年比一次copy 驚死你唔記得咁<br />\n<br />\n其實都幾灰"},{"pid":"d97339ea466394591912069a6d3a92e0f68ff4f3","tid":709640,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T07:58:15.000Z","msg":"人冇話冇左邊個唔得"},{"pid":"db033153f95dc022e89e58f719663edecdfa010f","tid":709640,"uid":133528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T08:00:06.000Z","msg":"Support Spain tonight<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/iran.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f6c8dea0952d4817acd8a98bdbadc3c6cc4e90a","tid":709640,"uid":189484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T08:11:53.000Z","msg":"我就黎要結婚喇<br />\n<br />\n但發現係唔完整既家庭入面長大, 係欠缺左一個榜樣, 由細到大都唔知甚麼係夫妻間既愛, 男女應該點樣才可以恒久相處, 久而久之, 連自己對家庭既價值觀好有問題.  <br />\n<br />\n而我對婚姻, 對伴侶, 對將來既信心, 亦都係好薄弱. 所以, 我決定唔生仔, 因為唔想將自己既不快經歷傳俾下一代, 佢地無權選擇係邊個家庭出世, 但我有權決定佢地黎唔黎呢個世界."},{"pid":"9d97a669cd72e4633eec3f9b4a5e859bddecf183","tid":709640,"uid":189484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d97339ea466394591912069a6d3a92e0f68ff4f3","tid":709640,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T07:58:15.000Z","msg":"人冇話冇左邊個唔得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T08:12:35.000Z","msg":"當你試過真係失去, 你就唔會咁講. <br />\n<br />\n我係過來人."},{"pid":"6253b79327b804a962e7407be1c78fe55c0794ef","tid":709640,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d97a669cd72e4633eec3f9b4a5e859bddecf183","tid":709640,"uid":189484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d97339ea466394591912069a6d3a92e0f68ff4f3","tid":709640,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T07:58:15.000Z","msg":"人冇話冇左邊個唔得"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T08:12:35.000Z","msg":"當你試過真係失去, 你就唔會咁講. <br />\n<br />\n我係過來人."},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T08:17:47.000Z","msg":"上個月死老豆"},{"pid":"8a1f5b007938004f3b21605168a741010e58748e","tid":709640,"uid":113678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1f6c8dea09